channel.title: Well you might aswell
channel.description:
I thought of a game while i was [s]masterbating[/s].... reading a book. I know everyone thinks the new updates are a crazy attempt to stop real world trading and autoing.
Pretty much what you do is, start out with "you might aswell"
and do something like
you might aswell take out bone burying, you need to dig a spade 50 times, read a page from the bible, then place the bones in the hole, if u fail, you lose the bones. Autoers lose.
GO AHEAD! TRY IT!
